com.canabang.genietext.core.model.io.xml
Interface XmlProperties

public interface XmlProperties

Contains the constant properties and values that will be used when parsing and generating XML files.

Version:
1.00 2009-03-14 Initial submission., 1.10 2009-05-31 Modified to handle addresses, stripped away all unnecessary constants. Changed this to an interface.
Author:
rhaq
